### Memory Management
- Pre-allocate tensor buffers to avoid dynamic allocation during inference
- Use object pooling for detection result objects to minimize GC pressure
- Release camera frames immediately after tensor conversion to prevent memory buildup

### Energy Considerations
- Run inference on the dedicated NPU/DSP when available (delegate to EdgeTPU, Neural Engine)
- Throttle to lower FPS (15) when the app is backgrounded or screen is off
