NoiseSuppressor.setStrength(0.7); // 0.0 (none) to 1.0 (aggressive)

// Listen for processed frames
NativeEventEmitter.addListener('onDenoisedFrame', (frame) => {
  // frame.data contains denoised audio samples
  audioSink.write(frame.data);
});

// Cleanup
await NoiseSuppressor.stop();
```

