Implement a NativeModule that exposes setBadge(count), getBadge(): Promise<number>, clearBadge(), and onBadgeChanged(callback). On iOS, update the badge on the main thread using UIApplication.sharedApplication.applicationIconBadgeNumber. On Android, use a launcher badge library like ShortcutBadger or provide a no-op fallback when unsupported.

